Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.67,0:01:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人类因人口膨胀而向宇宙移民已过了半个世纪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.26,0:01:43.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地球周围漂浮着巨大的人工都市
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.71,0:01:45.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作为人类的“第二故乡”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.37,0:01:52.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人们就在这里出生、成长、生儿育女\N并走向死亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.59,0:02:00.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙世纪0079年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.91,0:02:03.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,离地球最远的宇宙都市SIDE 3
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.43,0:02:04.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以ZION公国之名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.57,0:02:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,向地球联邦政府发起了独立战争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.13,0:02:11.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在开始一个月的战斗里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.35,0:02:16.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ZION公国和地球联邦军有半数以上的人口死去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.23,0:02:23.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人们对于自己的行为产生了恐惧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.93,0:02:35.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,‘荒野是战场’
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.22,0:02:51.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂！快撞山了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.93,0:03:07.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有人在副机舱里面吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.37,0:03:14.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小宝，你是男子汉来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.17,0:03:16.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎可以震荡一下便哭起来的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.51,0:03:19.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看，这里是地球！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.32,0:03:29.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亦是你爸爸生长出世的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.79,0:03:33.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你爸爸是很伟大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.36,0:03:35.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很值得你骄傲的好爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.86,0:03:42.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是否所有的母亲也是一样的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.43,0:03:45.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆罗，你有很久未见过妈妈呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.67,0:03:46.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.97,0:03:50.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆罗，队长找你啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.94,0:03:52.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢谢！哈罗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.05,0:03:57.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们真是胡来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.55,0:03:58.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,何不提高高度呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.92,0:04:01.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看不到敌机正在跟踪着吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.42,0:04:06.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以的话，我简直想在地上跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.89,0:04:10.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但起码可以找别人驾驶呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.23,0:04:11.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我做得来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.73,0:04:17.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里是侦察机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.03,0:04:19.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,木马正越过山脉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.14,0:04:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别让他们飞过去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.14,0:04:25.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快和地面的坦克联络一起进攻！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.38,0:04:25.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡尔玛！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.04,0:04:26.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么了，夏亚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.04,0:04:29.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你知道那母舰为何作这样的航行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.58,0:04:32.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可能是想避过雷达跟踪...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.18,0:04:34.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我看不是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.72,0:04:37.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们是想利用山脉来做防护网
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.65,0:04:39.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反过来展开防卫罩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.96,0:04:42.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,便是这样，即是说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.96,0:04:44.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里的粒子效果是绝大的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.96,0:04:48.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最好的追踪器也使用不出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.80,0:04:49.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,埋伏等他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.13,0:04:51.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找一处最有利的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.87,0:04:53.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然后来一次总攻击！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.21,0:04:57.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么一回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.87,0:04:59.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为何他们的战机会撤退呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.68,0:05:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定有原因的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.81,0:05:04.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们现在大峡谷地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.35,0:05:07.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而母舰的位置在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.25,0:05:12.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而敌人是想在湖边处攻击我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.79,0:05:14.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也有同感！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.72,0:05:17.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以这里是最不利的地点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.63,0:05:19.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今次的作战战果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.03,0:05:21.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就要全靠GUNDAM了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.66,0:05:23.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆罗，拜托了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.36,0:05:23.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.73,0:05:25.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他说我们无关重要啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.74,0:05:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,凯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.20,0:05:28.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.30,0:05:31.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,芙劳·波，他们想怎样呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.44,0:05:34.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,舰长，他们该无论如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.84,0:05:36.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也要和你相讨一下的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.98,0:05:38.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是这样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.85,0:05:40.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望你可以给我离开！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.08,0:05:42.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊！在这里离舰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.79,0:05:44.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在仍是备战状态啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.69,0:05:46.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前面有处地方叫圣乔治
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.16,0:05:48.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是我丈夫的故乡！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.93,0:05:50.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,故乡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.46,0:05:52.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在这里很难听到这名词的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.86,0:05:54.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明白你们是有难处的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.63,0:05:57.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我还是想带我的孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.80,0:05:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回乡下长大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.47,0:06:02.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们这班人实在太自私了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.97,0:06:03.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,布莱特！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.89,0:06:04.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,中尉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.61,0:06:06.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想到一个办法！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.58,0:06:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,办法？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.81,0:06:10.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！我向他们要求暂时停战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.21,0:06:11.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然后让他们下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.85,0:06:14.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊！好了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.42,0:06:19.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你认为如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.72,0:06:22.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们以难民离舰为理由宣布停战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.33,0:06:23.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,似乎是阴谋呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.09,0:06:25.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.33,0:06:28.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然不知这是什么用意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.20,0:06:30.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但可以拖延一下时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.80,0:06:31.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那又如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.17,0:06:33.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,行动较慢的陆战武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.94,0:06:35.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,便可以进行补给
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.74,0:06:39.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以战胜的比率也较高了，对吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.31,0:06:40.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.64,0:06:43.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他这种少爷脾性真是单纯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.78,0:06:45.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真天真！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.36,0:06:55.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么要炸毁它？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.06,0:06:57.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太可惜了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.06,0:06:59.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别吵了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.43,0:07:00.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们说不炸开一个洞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.83,0:07:02.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敌人是不会中计的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.96,0:07:31.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今次一定会嬴！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.73,0:07:35.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样也失败就太低能了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.00,0:08:09.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这飞机不会回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.03,0:08:10.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不后悔吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.17,0:08:12.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我早已下定了决心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.64,0:08:13.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无论怎样也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.17,0:08:16.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也要在地球抚养他成人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.37,0:08:18.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我这种心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.41,0:08:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大概你是不会明白的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.11,0:08:22.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我未在地球生活过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.15,0:08:24.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们来了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.35,0:08:25.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和我们预测一样呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.27,0:08:45.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是约翰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.74,0:08:47.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已确定White Base的运输机位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.07,0:08:49.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有可疑吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.51,0:08:52.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,机尾位置有中弹迹象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.04,0:08:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那些跟班飞机又来了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.41,0:08:56.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Hi！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.80,0:08:57.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.48,0:08:58.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别乱来！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.98,0:09:00.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你妒忌吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.25,0:09:01.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谁妒忌呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.68,0:09:02.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是担心计划会失败而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.72,0:09:09.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那小孩和我们挥手啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.13,0:09:21.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我印象中好像从没有个这么大的一个湖在这里...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.28,0:09:28.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那湖叫什么名字？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.95,0:09:30.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,似乎是被大型炸弹炸出来的呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.45,0:09:32.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那里降落吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.85,0:09:34.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里可看到四周
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.75,0:09:36.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,降落这里吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.99,0:09:42.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里有可居住的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.09,0:09:44.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就在这附近降落吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.63,0:09:45.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.72,0:09:46.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,开始行动！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.16,0:09:47.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.00,0:09:52.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就快可以了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.71,0:09:58.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看，好像在燃烧呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.84,0:10:00.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂！你们没事吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.04,0:10:02.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看来飞机故障了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.91,0:10:04.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都是你们不好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.55,0:10:05.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要紧急降落了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.44,0:10:06.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.15,0:10:09.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,总部通话，我是约翰...总部！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.29,0:10:12.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看来作留下的故障发作了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.79,0:10:14.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们的运气很差呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.09,0:10:16.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫他们继续监视行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.53,0:10:17.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.73,0:10:18.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有点不对呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.52,0:10:19.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.49,0:10:20.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,约定的地点到了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.73,0:10:24.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可能我过敏吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.53,0:10:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们正降低高度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.64,0:10:33.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要完成紧急降落，知道吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.54,0:10:35.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是了，我知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.74,0:11:02.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样子作战我就最喜欢了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.74,0:11:04.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们会上当吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.42,0:11:16.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老人四个、女人两个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.42,0:11:17.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小孩三个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.85,0:11:18.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一共是九个难民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.16,0:11:20.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,似乎不在里面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.59,0:11:21.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谁？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.52,0:11:24.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我还以为会有军人偷走呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.20,0:11:28.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们在监视他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.56,0:11:30.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那有可能走得掉呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.97,0:11:33.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你说得没错！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.34,0:11:38.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们先住到那面的民居去！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.47,0:11:40.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是一定要去圣乔治吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.88,0:11:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我认为路程不会太远的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.21,0:11:45.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但假苦找不到的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.58,0:11:47.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想会回来麻烦你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.12,0:11:49.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再见吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.46,0:11:55.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那对母子想去那里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.39,0:11:56.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再向前行也没有民居吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.19,0:11:59.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊！机长，你看！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.93,0:12:04.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,驾驶员要离开，他们正飞向母舰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.13,0:12:06.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要跟着去！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.61,0:12:11.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆罗，我们成功了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.97,0:12:13.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敌军已中计！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.57,0:13:15.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嘻，你看...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.58,0:13:20.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,照看是没问题的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.14,0:13:22.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要转回去！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.51,0:13:23.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在担心那对母子？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.01,0:13:25.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会被司令骂的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.82,0:13:27.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡尔玛上校还年轻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.68,0:13:30.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不会了解我们这年龄的人的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.59,0:13:32.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.04,0:13:47.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你突然干什么，良！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.70,0:13:49.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那侦察机又回来了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.70,0:13:50.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.78,0:13:54.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他要去那里！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.71,0:13:58.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,良 快打开舱门吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.97,0:14:22.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了！阿姆罗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.11,0:14:24.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你先躲在湖里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.64,0:14:27.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,待敌人进攻后便来个突袭！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.64,0:14:29.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆罗！你去那里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.40,0:14:31.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别用无线电
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.25,0:14:33.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刚才侦察机是向着那对母子飞去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.82,0:14:34.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有点不放心！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.23,0:14:35.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆罗！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.79,0:14:38.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一切顺利吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.89,0:14:39.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.82,0:14:41.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,过15分钟后就知道成不成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.06,0:14:43.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对了！凯！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.09,0:14:45.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有胆去试一试吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.63,0:14:47.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已经对那地形掌握了个大概
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.93,0:14:48.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,应该没问题的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.20,0:14:51.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,钢坦克，钢加农
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.23,0:14:52.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,开始准备！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.39,0:14:52.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.18,0:15:06.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,求求你们，救我的儿子！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.28,0:15:08.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找到了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.04,0:15:30.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别发现我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.08,0:15:38.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.18,0:15:39.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.78,0:15:41.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们再去查看一下！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.45,0:15:43.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先打开准备安全锁！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.12,0:15:48.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟！被发现了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.80,0:15:54.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是联邦军的机动战士？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.77,0:15:58.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不发现我就可以没事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.84,0:16:08.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,准备降落湖边！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.42,0:16:08.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.26,0:16:25.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和约翰失去了联络
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.23,0:16:26.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么一回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.53,0:16:29.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别理那侦察机，开始战斗！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.55,0:16:48.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你可否将高度降低！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.35,0:16:49.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.82,0:16:52.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太低的话母舰会撞向地面的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.79,0:16:54.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加油！凯！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.59,0:16:56.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只好一试了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.60,0:17:04.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到地面了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.24,0:17:11.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被瞄准着！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.94,0:17:45.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我...我不怕！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.58,0:17:48.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看！在湖边处的运输机那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.74,0:17:50.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有个机动战士出来了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.05,0:17:52.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,掩护我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.36,0:18:03.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没子弹？...糟了...用尽了子弹...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.66,0:18:07.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我军现在是背着湖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.93,0:18:09.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,面向敌军的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.37,0:18:10.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.47,0:18:12.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,坦克部队向前挺进了三公哩...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.70,0:18:18.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡尔玛！吩咐背着湖的机枪及坦克部队向前！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.67,0:18:19.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.88,0:18:22.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想那艘母舰捱不了多久呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.65,0:18:25.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但在湖边的运输机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.35,0:18:26.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会有敌军机动战士出现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.88,0:18:28.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我的话一定会这样做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.42,0:18:29.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏亚...？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.49,0:18:31.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们并没有检查过那一辆运输机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.05,0:18:34.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在岩石后面有机动战士？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.46,0:18:35.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真...真的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.89,0:18:38.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦？没可能的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.97,0:18:44.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊！阿姆罗！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.97,0:18:48.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是GUNDAM来了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.57,0:18:49.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,计划顺利进行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.04,0:18:51.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,GUNDAM正在敌军背面攻击！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.94,0:18:55.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好！火力集中在前面！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.85,0:18:56.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家听着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.55,0:18:58.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要将前面的马杰拉战车全部炸毁！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.91,0:19:33.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,气死人！打中自己人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.78,0:19:35.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停止攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.76,0:19:41.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没走得那么容易！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.68,0:20:03.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知那方战况如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.28,0:20:04.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.48,0:20:06.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,战争的胜负是难以估计的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.68,0:20:09.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无论谁会胜出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.55,0:20:12.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也会有很多女人像我般的不幸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.76,0:20:14.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,女人没了丈夫是很悲惨的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.36,0:20:17.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小宝，你睡着了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.14,0:20:28.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算GUNDAM如何利害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.74,0:20:30.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那么多敌人包围下也会输的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.47,0:20:59.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这么小的事，我也可以做得到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.44,0:21:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,凯！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.00,0:21:03.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敌人的新机动战士！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.35,0:21:17.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最后两台ZAKU被炸毁了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.05,0:21:19.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,总部，怎么办？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.02,0:21:22.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们的马杰拉战车部队已全灭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.13,0:21:24.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有任何可动的战车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.53,0:21:26.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,撤退，撤退啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.66,0:21:29.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好了..今次的损失惨重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.03,0:21:31.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫我如何向基西莉亚姐姐交待呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.17,0:21:34.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有机会挽回局面的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.70,0:21:35.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.64,0:21:38.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,指挥官一定要在前线才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.17,0:21:41.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下次我也要参加作战！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.11,0:21:43.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很多谢你！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.31,0:21:47.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们要返回基地了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.25,0:21:48.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想今晚你们最好睡在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.42,0:21:50.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我投下来的胶囊里吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.52,0:21:51.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多谢你们的帮忙呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.89,0:21:55.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小弟弟，你要坚强些保护母亲啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.09,0:21:57.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再见！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.57,0:22:04.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太太！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.93,0:22:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.60,0:22:10.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我记得这里以前是叫做圣乔治的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.27,0:22:12.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,照看你还是回去湖边那班同伴处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.14,0:22:14.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会比较好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.91,0:22:17.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊？这里就是...？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.68,0:22:22.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里就是...圣乔治...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.56,0:22:29.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小宝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.91,0:22:31.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妈妈！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.85,0:22:56.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那对母子不知道有否到达圣乔治
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:16.85,0:23:20.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡尔玛·萨比亲自对White Base发动攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:20.88,0:23:22.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,疲于战斗的阿姆罗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:22.88,0:23:27.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,提起精神操作GUNDAM而进行了空中战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.34,0:23:31.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们两人都不知道夏亚深奥的阴谋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.27,0:23:33.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,机动战士GUNDAM
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.67,0:23:35.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下一集 ‘飞吧！GUNDAM’
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:37.18,0:23:39.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你能够存活下去吗？

